OOC: I guess since it dosent belong to anyone (predaking is gone) I will
take the ship. Right now the computer in it is down, so I will post.

BIC:

The water is very tranquil, and the matching of dark purple metal
against the ocean floor would make for a beautiful paradis, if this ship
was not meant for destruction. Nothing on the ship made any moves, no
sign of energy could be detected from it. Again, there was silence.
